Fig.
 1.
 Experimental
 protocol.
 Graph
 branches
 specify
 the
 experimental
 sequence
 followed
 and
 the
 number
 of
 rats
 used
 in
 every
 test.
 CTRL,
 controls;
 LIR,
 Liraglutide;
 STZ,
streptozotocin;
 i.p.,
 intraperitoneal
 administration;
 i.c.v.,
 intracerebroventricular
 administration;
 s.c.,subcutaneously;
 FST,
 forced
 swimming
 test;
 EPM,
